        {
            "title": "綠心修訂供股條款   今復牌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">綠心集團(00094)修訂供股結構條款，股份今早復牌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240306_FI_HK-STOCK_source-licensed_shutterstock_fb-2.png.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240306_FI_HK-STOCK_source-licensed_shutterstock_fb-2.png.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公司宣布，由於經修訂供股結構不再設有額外申請安排，所有提及「額外申請」、「額外申請表格」及「額外供股股份」的內容均不再適用，並視為已從該公告中刪除。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">綠心昨公布供股集資，上午9時公司隨即停牌。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15006274-%e7%b6%a0%e5%bf%83%e4%bf%ae%e8%a8%82%e4%be%9b%e8%82%a1%e6%a2%9d%e6%ac%be-%e4%bb%8a%e5%be%a9%e7%89%8c",
